            <h2 class="heading">Our Story</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                    <img src="/img/about-us-image.jpg" alt="Furniro showroom" class="about-image" />
                </div>
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p class="description">
                        Founded in 2010, Furniro began as a small family-owned business with a passion for automotive excellence. Over the years, we've grown into a leading name in the industry, known for our commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction.
                    </p>
                    <p class="description">
                        Our journey has been driven by a simple yet powerful philosophy: to provide car enthusiasts with vehicles that not only meet but exceed their expectations. From classic models to cutting-edge designs, we've curated a collection that speaks to every automotive dream.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="our-mission">
            <h2 class="heading">Our Mission</h2>
            <div class="mission-content">
                <div class="mission-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-car"></i>
                    <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
                    <p>We rigorously test and inspect every vehicle to ensure it meets our high standards of performance and reliability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mission-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    <h3>Customer-Centric Approach</h3>
                    <p>Your satisfaction is our top priority. We strive to provide personalized service and support at every step of your journey with us.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mission-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                    <p>We're committed to reducing our environmental impact by promoting eco-friendly vehicles and sustainable practices.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
