                <p>Founder & CEO</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="/img/team-member-2.jpg" alt="Jane Smith" />
                <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                <p>Head of Design</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="/img/team-member-3.jpg" alt="Mike Johnson" />
